Package: adlibr
Title: Unified API Client for Ad Libraries Across Platforms
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Fabio", "Votta", , "fabio.votta@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3143-7315"))
Description: A comprehensive R client providing unified access to ad library APIs 
    across major platforms including Meta (Facebook/Instagram), TikTok, Microsoft 
    (Bing), Apple App Store, Amazon, Google (BigQuery datasets), and others. 
    Features OAuth 2.0 authentication, automatic pagination, rate limiting with 
    exponential backoff, and data normalization to a common schema. Designed for 
    researchers, journalists, and analysts studying digital advertising transparency.
